                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18110403-86-defend807 t18110403-86-punish516"></join>
               Whipped in Jail
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Second Middlesex jury, before Mr. Common Serjeant.</p>
